parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.How come I didn’t know about the wife?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.This doesn’t reopen the case. You’re digging for excuses.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlOp.Looks like we survived the trip over here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ll speak with Lillian and see what I can figure out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If you’re in any danger, I’ll let you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.I better go change into my uniform.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlEx.As I told you before… This place is very strange.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.What’s up, Lillian? Why did you invite me here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoEx.I must speak to you in private.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOpNo1.What the hell? That sounded like Erica!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.Sorry, Lillian. I was just taking a break with 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Channel 4 News was outside trying to interview the officers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.I don’t like all this company. This is exactly the kind of attention I didn’t want to bring to my late father’s legacy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Just how much do you know about this mansion, Lillian?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.I know my way around. It was my father’s, after all.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.He seems to have liked collecting artwork and artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.Do you still suspect he had connections to the Guild?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.Why are they here? What are you scheming?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeAnEx^.We’re here to save the nun, stupid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnDe^.You’re in over your head if you think you can deal with this alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.I’m putting a lot of trust in you, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoDe.I can’t explain it… Those men went into that orange glow… but then disappeared…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoWoEx.I looked inside, but the glow was gone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.It’s a gateway to Hell. You won’t find them if the gate is shut.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaDe.Go to the dining room. They’re waiting for you in the side room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Do you have access to that area?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.You can see it from the balcony.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.I fell!... 1Hero was helping me back up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx>.No need to leave right away, 1Hero. I only ask that you keep to the common areas.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlOp>.Don’t worry, Miss Abraham. I trust you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.Do you think she saw what we did?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.She’s playing dumb to keep us from being embarrassed…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaOp.I’m sorry, 1Hero. I don’t know what came over me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.I should be the one apologizing. I didn’t know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.I had this overwhelming urge for… sex.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t really know much, myself, but I hear that a virus is going around that causes heightened libido.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.Do you think this mansion has the virus in it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Whatever it is I just saw, it’s not normal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Let’s not get ahead of ourselves. I need to research this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.I want to know more about this virus too…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Oh, uhh... I just moved in. It’s pretty empty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlEx.We’re going to need a place to meet to discuss our… research.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoClNo1.1Hero! What happened to that poor girl?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I don’t know… I was going to ask you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.And the pain?… It was located in her… nether regions?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArShCl.This is so much different than I expected.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.Where I am from, we do not suffer pain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.But I am glad to see that you’re willing to offer a healing touch.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Arianna… Do you see everything that I do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Sorry about that, Lillian. We had an emergency and had to rush out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Does Detective Bhatt still want my father’s files? Because I could not find any recent records.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You know, I think if she’s still interested, she’ll contact you directly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s nothing to know. Your father had some connections with an illegal organization many years ago…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.But I wouldn’t worry too much about it. The case is almost closed and soon there will be no more Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.I look forward to leaving this part of his life behind and remembering the father I loved.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Sorry about that, Lillian. We had an emergency and had to rush out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Does Detective Bhatt still want my father’s files? Because I could not find any recent records.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You know, I think if she’s still interested, she’ll contact you directly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s nothing to know. Your father had some connections with an illegal organization many years ago…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.But I wouldn’t worry too much about it. The case is almost closed and soon there will be no more Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.I look forward to leaving this part of his life behind and remembering the father I loved.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.I saw your news broadcast… You found a painting?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.You’ve been snooping around the mansion, 1Hero. You can’t deny it now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Lillian… I don’t know everything that’s going on. But Duncan is about to get taken down…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Maybe it’s time you start sharing more with me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoAnOp.You’ve earned her trust with little effort… Consider yourself lucky.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I take it no one got caught.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.Thank you for inviting us, Lillian. I look forward to getting to know you better.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.You’re always welcome in my home, Erica. And, 1Hero, thank you for coming.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’ll be nice to spend an evening with two lovely ladies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.Let me show you the dining room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Just checking in. Seems the news is now trying to get info from the police outside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaEx.Lillian isn’t happy with the new company.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.I like it. Makes me feel safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.I’ve not seen her for a while…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.It’s a broken key, but it’s covered in moss.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.No… it was in the dining room, under the table.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There is… but I’ve already seen it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.Maybe you can find the other half of the key. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoOp.I’ve never felt like that before… What did you do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What did I do?... I have no idea… It’s the rock!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErShEx.The witch idol! It messed with our minds!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No… We were literally floating… I felt it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiHaOp.What an incredible find. That artifact must be very valuable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.Artifacts with magic powers… Like this one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.One looks like a hand, and this one looks like a leg.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.These are parts of a bigger witch idol. My grandma told me about them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Please do not lose this. It certainly has great value.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.Do you think your father might have had other ones like it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Not that I’ve seen. But I would be very curious to see the completed idol.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.If what I know is true, the other pieces should be nearby.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.If you’d like, you can keep the pieces with me. I can protect them in my safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Thanks for the offer, but I should keep them for evidence. It’s not legal to collect Casula artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’ve got special privileges… I’ll keep them safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaDe.Seems like you’re pretty interested in these artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiHaEx.If they can produce effects such as what we’ve just experienced, I would be quite interested in seeing these pieces…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.Perhaps I could acquire the necessary permits to purchase them from you, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.That’s not entirely true. There are licenses for that kind of thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I will. But for now I better get back to work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.Don’t forget to stop by my place tonight, 1Hero…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlDe.You have to help me break in.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.She locked herself out of her apartment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.You are welcome to stay with me, Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFlEx.Thanks for the offer, but I think 1Hero can handle it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.Do you think she knows about the witch idol?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Hard to tell. I expected she’d mention something, but maybe she really doesn't know anything about that hidden chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoDe.Would you really sell her the artifacts?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I was just trying to get information…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.But I do know a guy who can buy them legally.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.I’ll keep an eye out for more pieces.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Be careful. We don’t know what they do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.There’s a hidden room in the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I’m not surprised. How is this relevant?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaEx.The search warrant was for a storage area, under the front of the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaBaOp.My guess is that Charles would hide anything Guild related down there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnEx.She left a while ago. Be ready. And don’t tell your girlfriend what we know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ve not mentioned the stolen amulets. She doesn’t know anything except what was in the police reports.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.I take it 1Hero has told you the news.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Then you know that we’re here to look into the possible connections your father had with the Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaEx.It is shocking to hear that he may have dealt with a criminal organization…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.But he was a man with many acquaintances.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrEx^.Don’t worry, Miss Wilkes. It was many years ago and no charges were pressed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.I hate to be a bother, but could you retrieve your father’s business files? We'd love to take a look at them at the station.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.Do we have a warrant for that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaOp.I’d love to help, but what are you looking to find?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp^.I don’t know if you’re aware, but we’ve been very active in taking down the Eclipse Guild recently.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.If your father had connections, we’d be able to apprehend more suspects.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaEx.I don’t want my father’s name to be associated with them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrEx.Whatever we find, we will not take action against your father. We only care about taking down the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Hey, I’m just looking out for us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.I know what I’m doing, 1Hero. Don’t forget that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I wasn’t able to get any information from Lillian. She seems to be surprised to hear about her father’s possible Guild connections.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Then do you really think she’s going to bring us anything that will help?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I don’t expect so. I’m buying us time…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Yeah, it is. We should split up. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaFrEx.Sounds like a plan. Bobby, you go left. 1Hero, you take the stairs to the right…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Stop complaining. Let’s hurry. This isn’t like her to just disappear.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.You guys check the stairs on the left.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.Not at all. How can we help you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp>.That man you saw was Duncan Helmer. He’s a criminal art thief.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx>.He likely knew you were alone and was targeting you for an easy take.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.It's disheartening to know that such a man would show interest in my home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx>.Would you both be able to come down to the station to make statements?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe>.Experience has taught us that even the smallest details can break a case wide open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaOp.I must decline, if that’s alright. I’d hate to leave the mansion with so many guests present.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.However, Erica, you are free to take the rest of the day off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx^.Sure, I’d be happy to help however I can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrOp>.Yes, thank you both. I hope we see you at the station soon, Miss Wilkes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I’ll be there in just a moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiHaOp.Thank you again, 1Hero, for being here for us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’m just happy no one got hurt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I hate to think what might have happened if I hadn’t shown up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.I was just thinking the same thing. I must admit, the thought of you being near is comforting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Beyond that, your company means a lot. Perhaps you and I can get to know each other more intimately.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.You’re a beautiful woman. I think I’d like that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp.Thank you, Lillian. I’ll be sure to call you soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.If you think of anything that Duncan could be targeting, please let us know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.There are many pieces here in the mansion, but if something stands out as unusual, I’ll call you right away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I should get going. I don’t want to leave Miss Bhatt waiting for too long.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Erica was late this morning. I hope the events of yesterday have not rattled her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShOp.Is that Lillian?... I hear something coming from the next room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HoBaEx.Madam Wilkes is preoccupied at the moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Oh, shit! I gotta get out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.1Hero. Where are all the officers? There’s only one left?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.1Hero. Erica. So nice to see you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Hi, Lillian. I was just… coming to warn you that the police presence has been reduced.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.As much as I appreciate getting back some privacy, I must ask: Is it safe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.If anything comes up, the police will be here fast… Don’t worry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.What about you, Miss Abraham? Do you feel safe here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.I won’t keep you from your work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.Are you telling me Madalyn is still here in the mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I saw her! She was talking about looking for… the Toma and the Amulets… and…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.Slow down. She’s looking for the Toma Leolo?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Yeah… The pieces… She’s looking for them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.Are you sure? You’re talking about the thing that made us float, right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Yeah… Madalyn must have had a piece… It had an effect on her too… It’s hard to explain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.What the hell am I supposed to do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.No shit. But what if that devil woman comes after me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.So you still want me spying on Lillian?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.Do we? Are you sure about this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Come on. I still have the holy water bomb. Maybe we can find her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.It’s weird. You have to hear it for yourself…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.This metal box is secured by a rusty lock and chain. Even if I had a key, it probably wouldn’t work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my hacksaw to cut through the chain!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I was hoping to steal Erica away from you tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Well… We’re having a little party over at Chloe’s place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErSaDe^.I don’t know if I can go…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.You can leave early, Erica. It won't be a problem.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErHaOp^.Really? Thanks, Lillian. That’s very kind of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.I appreciate the offer, but I must stay here and tend to things.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Same with Sister Judy… Oh, and Hannah.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.Go on, Erica. You’re free to leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlEx.You’ve been up to something, and I’ve been watching.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Lillian… I don’t know what you’re talking about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.Do you really think I’ve been blind to your actions?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I… I just want to know what’s happening here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.This is a house of worship, 1Hero. It’s a place for service to the Lord.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The men that are here… Where did they come from?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.They have been here for a long, long time. Serving under my father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.They are servants to the Lord and nothing else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t get it. What’s the point of this? Do you expect me to believe this is some sort of charity for the sick?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.That’s exactly what it is. But not in a way I’d expect you to understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFlOp.There’s something I can show you… Something that will open your eyes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrEx.Come by this evening… After your party…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.I’m heading home for a bit. I’ll see you tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.I’ll head over with her in a bit…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.It’s nothing… I’ll see you at the party. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Sounds like someone is in the next room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.Wait!... We can spy on them from the balcony.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Where the hell do you think you’re going?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.This place is beautiful… I must admit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.It’s big... But not as nice as the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrCl.You’re kind to say that… But I feel the beauty of the church is wearing thin for me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You’re choosing your own way, Judy… What do you want in life?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrCl.I’ve held it inside for so long…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaEx.I want to be a mother… I want to raise a child of my own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I think you’d make for a great mother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.You are a brave man, 1Hero… And a kind man.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.You know, Judy… There’s still plenty of time to kill before the others show up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFlOp.I do wonder if the bedroom is as nice as this entryway suggests.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrOp.1Hero… Where would I be the most helpful?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFrEx.If I see anything, I’ll let you know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.Well, if it isn’t Detective Canmore… Nice of you to join us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.A gold one with a green gem, a silver one with a black gem, and a silver one with a yellow diamond.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.And this will stop Lillian from using the Toma?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Well… Something like that… I don’t know exactly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnDe.This all sounds crazy, but I can’t turn a blind eye. There’s something fishy happening here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Ella and Nellie are helping search, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Judy and Kimberly didn’t know where they ended up… But I know that they are in the mansion…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Well… I hope they are in the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.They could take a long time to find.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Nevermind that. Everyone, spread out and start looking.");
